The '''Vaynai Archipelago''' was the main landmass on the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] resort [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Vaynai/Legends|Vaynai]]. Made up of a series of large mesas, the island chain included [[Streysel Island]], among others. While the rich businesses and resorts of that world were built on top of the mesa-islands themselves, the poor were relegated to a series of artificially-created caverns that were carved throughout the high outcroppings.

